The paper deals with the problem of answering a sequence of queries about a dataset, which is a common problem in computer science research. The use of differential privacy and the analysis of algorithms suggest that the paper could belong to the categories of cryptography (cs.CR), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), machine learning (cs.LG), information theory (cs.IT), or artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
